  • Type Parameters:

    All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface View<V>
    A View provides a common general enumerable view of an object. The following loop illustrates the means to enumerate the view: 
     for (Object k : aView.keySet())
 {
   V value = aView.get(k);
 }

    jdh
